  TextAlignment->Center,ExpressionUUID->
  "417c92c5-30c3-e143-bb2f-c360900c9bbd"],
 " be ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["G", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "047594d2-059b-4148-9900-169f022f2d70"],
 "-irreps. Then"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.96307688737154*^9, 3.963076923816498*^9}, {
