32a2bbab6f88"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[TextData[{
 "Theorem (Isotypic decomposition of the tensor product of multiple ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["G", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d6606b09-1845-c04c-ad22-319a377e0ad8"],
